title: The Gary Null Show
content:
Guest: Evelyn Pringle Evelyn Pringle is an award-winning investigative journalist focused on exposing corruption in... <!--more--> government and corporate America.
Over the past 7-8 years, she has written numerous exposes on the psychopharmaceutical complex with a focus on the government-drug maker cartel with a mission to over-medicate children and very young in the US.
In 2009 she aided US Senator Grassley’s office for compiling data on TeenScreen and the pharmaceutical front organizations pushing for the drugging of children.
 Her most recent articles on the psychoactive drugging of infants and toddlers has been sponsored by the International Center for the Study of Psychiatry and Psychology.
